Package: bankdata
Type: Package
Title: Forensic Tools for Banking Data
Version: 0.1.0
Author: person(given = "Samuel",
             family = "Meichtry",
             role = c("auth","cre"),
             email = "samuel.meichtry@swisslancer.com",
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2165-791X"))
Maintainer: The package maintainer <samuel.meichtry@swisslancer.com>
Description: Preparation of bank records for forensic analysis. Create layouted OCR text from PDF documents. Different Text manipulation functions. Retrieving transactions (text to column for a given header, parsing with regular expressions, etc.). Retrieving structured information (IBANs, ISINs, Credit Cards, etc.). Collection of Open Source Intelligence (OSINT) Tools. 
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggested:
  dplyr,
  tidyr,
  pdftools,
  writexl,
  readxl,
  jsonlite,
  curl,
  httr
